---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 157
  - Title: Shekel Hakodesh
    Location: 175
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Renunciation-Detachment=Spiritual Poverty
---
He who with little is well content is rich indeed as a king; and a king, in
his greatness, is poor as the pedlar, when his kingdom sufficeth him not.
